## Limitations & Considerations

### Data Constraints
- **Survival bias**: Analysis limited to documented passengers
- **Missing data**: 20% of age records unavailable
- **Historical context**: Social norms of 1912 may not reflect modern scenarios

### Analytical Assumptions
- Random missing data patterns (validated through exploration)
- Independence of passenger decisions (limited by family group dynamics)
- Consistent reporting accuracy across passenger classes

